_sText:
dod_jagdy is a port with cuted of the official dod_jagd map from Day of Defeat: Source game.

Description of the original map:

June 1944, Suburb of Caen. 

The British army, advancing towards Caen, is blocked in the city of Villers-Bocage by a German armored division. 

Things take an even worse turn when the Khorsa glider, heading for Caen, crashes into enemy territory.
